## Legal Basis (GDPR - If applicable)

For users in the European Economic Area (EEA):
- **Consent**: We process location data with your explicit consent
- **Legitimate Interest**: We process device data for app functionality
- **Right to Withdraw**: You can withdraw consent by disabling location in settings

## California Privacy Rights (CCPA - If applicable)

California residents have the right to:
- Know what personal information is collected
- Delete personal information
- Opt-out of the sale of personal information (we do NOT sell data)

---

## Summary

**What we collect**: Your location (GPS coordinates), device information, advertising identifier  
**Why we collect it**: To show sunset/sunrise times and directions, display advertisements  
**Where it's stored**: Locally on your device only (location data), Google AdMob may collect advertising data  
**Who we share with**: Only Google Maps (for displaying maps) and Google AdMob (for advertisements)  
**Your control**: You can delete saved locations anytime, disable location in settings, limit ad tracking, or uninstall the app
